  "short_description": "Ride the waves in Tidekeeper, a strategy adventure game where you guide Fin and Chumby to help the residents of the Hourglass Isles. Master the art of scheduling to maximize your impact as you assist islanders, complete time-sensitive tasks, and dive into a variety of fun and engaging minigames.",
